text: Julien Benneteau and Édouard Roger-Vasselin were the defending champions, but Benneteau decided not to participate this year. Roger-Vasselin played alongside Nicolas Mahut and successfully defended his title, defeating Ken and Neal Skupski in the final, 6–1, 7–5. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Moselle Open - Doubles Category:Moselle Open
title: 2018 Moselle Open – Doubles
